				</header>

				
				<section class="comment post-content">
					<div class="comment-text"><p>Great post, and I think this is the gem of the lot. It summarizes the entire set of thoughts while smacking you upside the head: &#8220;Could your Strong Female Character be seamlessly replaced with a floor lamp with some useful information written on it to help a male hero?&#8221;</p>
<p>Rock on!</p>
</div>				</section>

